@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.58
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.12 / v2 + 0.02) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.48)))
    tmp = v2
    v0 = 0.54
    v1 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v2 = wp.cos(0.53)
    data[tid] = v0
